These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, cola
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, avocado, plum
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie, scientific
There are 3 different nationalities: french, chinese, japanese
3 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, horse
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, bike, jet-ski
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the french##1
5. the chinese is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person eating zucchini is between the owner of the hamster and the person eating avocado##2
8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola     | sprite      | water      |
| Food          | avocado   | zucchini   | plum       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | martial-arts | zombie    |
| Nationality   | japanese  | french    | chinese    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig    | horse    | hamster |
| Transport     | bike  | jet-ski     | roller        |

