.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, eggplant, lettuce
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, family, romance
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, egyptian
3 different pets are kept: frog, dog, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, volleyball, surfing
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the person eating lettuce is between the egyptian and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
7. the person watching family movies is between the person watching romance movies and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea     | mirinda        | hot-chocolate      |
| Food          | eggplant    | lettuce       | nectarine  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | family | action    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | canadian   | indonesian    |
| Pet           | dog      | frog  | rabbit      |
| Sport         | surfing    | volleyball      | handball |

