.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, apple, cranberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, gospel, ambient
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, british, italian
3 different pets are kept: horse, goat, bird
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, train, roller
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the italian and the owner of the horse##2
2. the british is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the spanish is the spanish##1
4. the owner of the bird is the fan of gospel##1
5. the british is on the left of the fan of soul##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person eating lettuce##2
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
8. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
9. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | lettuce  | apple    | cranberry   |
| Hobby         | fishing | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | ambient       | gospel    | soul |
| Nationality   | italian    | british  | spanish  |
| Pet           | goat     | bird   | horse       |
| Transport     | train | scooter     | roller       |

