2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the indian##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person eating nectarine and the person driving the airplane##2
9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | milk     | almond-milk      |
| Food          | nectarine     | pineapple     | apricot     |
| Hobby         | reading      | woodworking | sudoku    |
