4. the nigerian is on the far right##1
5. the fan of rock is the owner of the cat##1
6. the coach is between the person eating asparagus and the owner of the hedgehog##2
7. the colombian is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
8. the accountant is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |      2       |       3       |
