2. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the car and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the fan of metal##1
8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | tea   | almond-milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports  | musical  |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | reggae  | jazz        |
| Pet           | rat       | dog   | mouse |
| Sport         | golf      | water-polo | cricket   |
| Transport     | jet-ski   | skateboard     | car |

 